To insert record 
url: http://localhost:8081/api/create
Request method : POST
json {
    "firstName":"nivetha",
    "lastName":"mohan",
    "emailId":"nivetha@gmail.com",
    "age":"28",
    "gender":"female",
    "address":"23sva anada bangalore"
}

To update record
url : http://localhost:8081/api/update
Request method :POST
json {
    "id":1,
    "firstName":"prachi",
    "lastName":"priya prasad",
    "emailId":"prachi@gmail.com",
    "age":"22",
    "gender":"female",
    "address":"23sva anada  nilayabangalore"
}

To find all non deleted records
url : http://localhost:8081/api/findAll
RequestMethod  : GET

To find all deleted records
url :http://localhost:8081/api/findAllDeletedRecords
Request method :GET

To find a particular record by id
url: http://localhost:8081/api/findById/1
Request method :GET

To delete a record by id
url :http://localhost:8081/api/deleteById/1
Request method: GET
